Title: If a Gem Isn't Pretty
Description:
The kith of Loamm request the skills of a jewelcrafter! I have seen the wondrous sparkling gems in this glorious city, and the niffen below wish to see them as well. We don't see very well, so we know the value of a good sparkle!

Our chief Gemfinder and Jewelshiner, Miss Fanilly, wishes to see some beautiful gems. I bet she'd love the ones named after Alexstrasza and Ysera!

Please deliver them to Loamm as soon as you can, won't you?
ObjectivesText: Deliver Silken Gemdusts, Alexstraszites and Ysemeralds to Fanilly in Loamm.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Deliver the items to Fanilly in Loamm
